ISLAMABAD, Jan 21 (APP): Special Assistant to the Prime Minister on Political Communication Dr Shahbaz Gill on Friday said Prime Minister Imran Khan would receive direct phone calls in a programme “Your Prime Minister” from the public around 3 pm Sunday.
The prime minister would listen to the complaints and opinions of the people, and would also inform them about the steps taken by the government, he tweeted.
